WEBVTT

00:00.513 --> 00:04.027
One World Observatory at the top of One World Trade Center,...

00:04.431 --> 00:06.093
...the crowning jewel of the skyline.

00:06.830 --> 00:10.127
Ascend to the top of the tallest building in the Western Hemisphere...

00:10.648 --> 00:12.438
...in less than 60 seconds.

00:13.168 --> 00:16.457
Look toward the horizon and feel the city's invincible spirit.

00:17.571 --> 00:21.093
Experience three floors filled with innovation and inspiration...

00:21.709 --> 00:27.685
...from the See Forever Theater to the expansive Sky Portal...

00:28.125 --> 00:30.602
...for a walk high above the streets of New York.

00:31.579 --> 00:34.756
Connect with the bustling crossroads of the world with City Pulse...

00:35.585 --> 00:40.226
...and enjoy extraordinary dining and amenities available only to observatory guests.

